title: Playmate of the Year: Collection - The '90s
overview: They're the beauties that defined a decade, and now Playboy revisits 10 Playmates of the Year including favorites Jenny McCarthy, Anna Nicole Smith, Victoria Silverstedt, Stacy Sanches and more! Discover them all over again in these intimate introductions as Playboy chronicles their earliest beginnings and uncovers that special something that made them unforgettable the first time.
